{"tid":125094,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇大家食 食食?","createTime":"2017-02-18T07:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T02:29:35.000Z","uid":56524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8811cac5c6f0665a6144b2e5b6218484ad4b6350","tid":125094,"uid":56524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T07:30:26.000Z","msg":"日日J<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n概念圖<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/18/153017_964d5b1ed9aa2699cd622f9e2df60739.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F153017_964d5b1ed9aa2699cd622f9e2df60739.jpg&h=04b3d014&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3c7f912cff28ca967ee96ecffd9a55f041d68c9","tid":125094,"uid":71694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T11:31:27.000Z","msg":"......"},{"pid":"ad2e0ea95d51561e30234c8d50ec0cad28a7eae3","tid":125094,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44a2dbed18d16d49a9fb3c163afcdea91839e87c","tid":125094,"uid":2485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T12:25:49.000Z","msg":"我認為呂以村先生既才能勁過肯德基伯伯<br />\n<br />\n肯德基伯伯淨係識整雞<br />\n<br />\n呂以村先生才華洋溢<br />\n<br />\n識整手攪面，村村住家窩面，過山雞，滷大腸，十三會<br />\n<br />\n求其一種都獨當一面<br />\n<br />\n相比肯德基淨係識整雞<br />\n<br />\n而我認為除非譚仔同佢三哥聯手<br />\n<br />\n否則呂以村先生單打獨鬥下必輕取二人<br />\n<br />\n呂以村先生贏過食神挑戰賽第二<br />\n<br />\n你可能話，<br />\n<br />\n點解贏唔到第一？<br />\n<br />\n因為呂先生既大絕手攪面當年仲未完成<br />\n<br />\n如今呂先生既手攪面已經獨霸美食界<br />\n<br />\n每條面都用捕獲等級4200既奇蹟小麥精製<br />\n<br />\n手攪面以呂先生既80G臂力攪成<br />\n<br />\n其QQ程度無法抗拒<br />\n<br />\n每次步入大家食<br />\n<br />\n我必先淨身<br />\n<br />\n帶著感恩敬佩之心<br />\n<br />\n斗膽地去order酸辣十三會手攪面走芽菜<br />\n<br />\n我只有三十五之齡<br />\n<br />\n卻能有幸品嚐千年難得之美食<br />\n<br />\n十三會，每一會都獨當一面<br />\n<br />\n肉菜均衡<br />\n<br />\n請容我續一介紹：<br />\n<br />\n蘿蔔，甜美可口<br />\n<br />\n吸收左美味湯汁，再混和蘿蔔本身味道<br />\n<br />\n人間極品<br />\n<br />\n腩肉，肥瘦相隔<br />\n<br />\n放在舌尖上<br />\n<br />\n油脂溶化，瘦肉有咬口<br />\n<br />\n兩者就像太極之道<br />\n<br />\n相生相克<br />\n<br />\n味道之中感悟人生大道理<br />\n<br />\n過山雞，聽聞呢味菜係呂先生人生第一次玩過山車時諗出來既<br />\n<br />\n食過山雞尤似坐過山車<br />\n<br />\n時而平穩，時而刺激<br />\n<br />\n過山雞外層略脆味濃<br />\n<br />\n刺激味覺神經<br />\n<br />\n內裡肉質鮮嫩多汁<br />\n<br />\n味道穩健充實<br />\n<br />\n每次食過山雞<br />\n<br />\n必然回想起人生跌盪<br />\n<br />\n亦想起呂先生沉實敦厚既外型<br />\n<br />\n大家見面大家食<br />\n<br />\n大家食面見大家 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家記住<br />\n<br />\n無呂以村先生人像商標<br />\n<br />\n果間唔係真既大家食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一次不來你錯過<br />\n<br />\n兩次不來我過錯<br />\n<br />\n來吧<br />\n<br />\n怕去食大家食"},{"pid":"6a467b38055352a6f95ade32f5ba5035c2755358","tid":125094,"uid":21358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:19:12.000Z","msg":"好撚好食 屌打譚仔"},{"pid":"1d3fc0cf00d7ab3cdf62b537b372b7ff611f3748","tid":125094,"uid":19738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:27:59.000Z","msg":"金槍人呂生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2234a4c9e165868fd3059ffb90d6fe4e15a34299","tid":125094,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T02:29:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係大家食J<br />\n要認住老細個樣同佢碌J"}]}